%% Availability Engine — shared computation, NOT a user-facing workflow.
%% Called by booking-management (validate a slot, suggest slots) and public-booking (search, hold).
%% Single rule of truth: availability is derived from SCHEDULED blocks only.
%% Completing a booking early does NOT free its remaining time.
%%
%% Inputs: service(s) + duration each, requested staff (specific or "any"), date/time or date range.
%% Config pulled from settings + staff-management:
%%   business hours, blackout dates, buffer; per-staff working hours, breaks, time off, capabilities;
%%   existing scheduled bookings; min lead time.
flowchart TD
    Start([Request]) --> Mode{Mode?}
    Mode -->|Validate a specific slot| ValidateIn[Proposed start + service set + staff]
    Mode -->|Search open slots| SearchIn[Date range + service set + staff pref]

    %% --- Resolve which staff can serve each service ---
    ValidateIn --> Capable
    SearchIn --> Capable[For each service:<br/>candidate staff = capability ∩ requested<br/>'any' = all capable staff]
    Capable --> AnyNote[/"any available": a slot is open if ≥1 capable staff is free;<br/>the actual person is assigned later by an Admin at confirm/]
    AnyNote --> Cap0{Any capable staff?}
    Cap0 -->|No| NoStaff[No one can perform this service] --> Empty([Return: unavailable / no slots])

    %% --- Build each candidate staff's free windows for the day(s) ---
    Cap0 -->|Yes| FreeWin[Build free windows per staff:<br/>business hours ∩ staff working hours]
    FreeWin --> Subtract[Subtract unavailable time:<br/>blackout dates, time off, breaks,<br/>existing bookings each padded by buffer,<br/>active (unexpired) slot holds]
    Subtract --> Lead[Drop time earlier than now + min lead time]
    Lead --> Branch{Single or multi-service?}

    %% --- Single service ---
    Branch -->|Single| Fit1[Need a free window ≥ duration + buffer]

    %% --- Multi-service ---
    Branch -->|Multi, sequential| Seq[Same staff free for a CONTIGUOUS block =<br/>sum of durations + inter-service buffers]
    Branch -->|Multi, parallel| Par[Each service's staff free during the<br/>OVERLAPPING visit window]
    Fit1 --> ModeSplit
    Seq --> ModeSplit
    Par --> ModeSplit

    %% --- Diverge by mode ---
    ModeSplit{Validate or Search?}

    %% Validate path
    ModeSplit -->|Validate| Check{Proposed slot fits<br/>all constraints?}
    Check -->|Yes| OK([Return: available])
    Check -->|No| Conflict([Return: conflict + reason])

    %% Search path
    ModeSplit -->|Search| Gen[Generate candidate starts<br/>across free windows at 15-min interval]
    Gen --> Collect[Union across staff,<br/>dedupe start times, sort]
    Collect --> Any{Any slots?}
    Any -->|Yes| Slots([Return: ranked open slots])
    Any -->|No| Empty
